Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:22.62,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:28.25,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:31.21,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.21,0:22:34.09,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:39.28,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:46.19,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:51.57,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:58.45,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.03,0:23:04.87,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:14.06,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:19.26,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:22.31,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:25.35,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:30.88,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm home!\NI've returned home, everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait though... \NI'm still feeling kinda dull somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm home, dad, mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For making you worry, I apologize.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reckon I'll start with stating things as it is, \Ncome what may.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom then will surely start wailing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And dad, I believe, will flip out instantly. \NHe has every reason for that after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet I can return as if nothing happened, \Nsay hello and head upstairs to the room immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay inside for a while, \Nobserving the situation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whichever the way I choose, \NI will remain guilty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wasn't even close to Karuizawa. \NI went to New York overseas!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I'm back..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever has happened before, I'm back now. \NAnd I'm going to my home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going home where my mom and dad are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Goemon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're glad you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Or would you prefer coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the tea is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a little longer for supper, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've made you so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, the bath! \NWould you mind preparing a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NThe bath is such a joy after a trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:33.26,Default,,0,0,80,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HAC907F&\t(0,1000,\bord0\blur0.55)\c&HFEFEFD&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\3a&H2D&\fscx184\fscy156}Episode 8 \N\N\N\N\NThe final                                     \h
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:33.26,Default,,0,0,30,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HAC907F&\t(0,1000,\bord0\blur0.55)\c&HFEFEFD&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\3a&H2D&\fscx184\fscy156}\h            repêchage Match... {\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wine! \NYou know, like a souvenir from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And... it is delicious... Must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, starting tomorrow, \NI will return to practices!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And for being such a nuisance, \NI'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for you being a woman, \NI'd give you a blow that'd deform your skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside, we need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,An international women's tennis tournament \Nwill be held next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the participants are soon-to-be pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Only two amateurs from Japan will participate - \NRyuzaki and, Oka, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're once again to withdraw before actually starting, \Nmake me know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, for today, you're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me participate,\Nwhatever the cost, I'm begging.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, you should take a sip too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see. \NYou really are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.\NI was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so much to ask you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all that giggling? \NA reward substitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good Lord, you're in Japan for less than a day, \Nbut already have the game scheduled?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, aren't you overworking yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? Know what, \NI'm more eager about returning to tennis than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that{\i0} is the reason behind that glowing!\NGreat, great! Hiromi is doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, so, did everything go well between you and Todo? \NI demand a full report with ins and outs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:13.94,Default,,0,0,1,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Contemporary European Art \N{\fs15}Winter women's clothing commission shop, 3rd floor of the main building
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo was doing just well. \NThe report is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that so stingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it two, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.43,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Okonomiyaki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more important, in America I did it for the first time. \NI believe now my letters will start reaching Todo's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how to express it, but somehow it feels now, \Nthat even when we are far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo is always somewhere nearby, \Nvery close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a red thread connection?\NNaughty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that, I almost forgot! \NHere, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A souvenir. Maki, you've been helping me \Nso much with this adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, how most sudden!\NCan I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I describe that colour if not "sexy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which may only mean you've finally \Nmade up your mind to something decisive, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have everything ready for you, \Ncoach Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful. \NOka is also to come here soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Hiromi \Nreturned from New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I returned home the night before yesterday.\NAnd I must say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- I sincerely...\N- Did you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you fix things up for the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you manage to relieve his soul? \NTo bring him to peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God... I was so terribly worried \Nthat you could not make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in. \NCoach Katsura is already waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... Ms. Ryuzaki, I am... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest, now come...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you can see \Na guest player from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gene Ryder, 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the tournament's challengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Queen's Cup tennis tournament \Nwill be her first professional event this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, all most promising new players \Nare from overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She is among the players \Non whom the whole world's eyes are currently gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to her natural talents,\Nshe is also credited with possessing the valuable "Hungry Spirit."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means the stronger her opponent gets, \Nthe more vigorous is her play. That is the type of player she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gene Ryder - don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, there is one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Spanish Marchesa Broir, 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she finished second \Nat that year's Australia Open Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, they're all very young, \Nbut their play is sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Both parents are former pro-players. \NFrom infancy, these skills were engendered in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are first-class sources of young energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For their reflexes and instantaneous strength, \Nthey were immediately called geniuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This video should \Nmake a great help for us next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you to give them a warm welcome, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand pardons \Nfor all the trouble you had to come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I will make the best of every opportunity \Nto obtain materials like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in my interest for both Oka and Reika to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo has entered the pro-path before any of you, \Nbut he'll still have to struggle for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Ozaki has left the battlefield once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,More than whenever the Japanese tennis world \Nis in need of some momentum now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I believe that it's for you two to set it in motion. \NUnleash your potential and show everyone a wonderful play!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the only believing in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our girl... went abroad all alone \Nand returned here, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "so what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already 19, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's {\i1}still{\i0}... just 19...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one proven \Nold colleague of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this gentleman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a tennis club coach, \Nmaking worthy players of promising university students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And a word is that since last week, \Nthis colleague conducts two-week training courses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If going under his command for a while is fine with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,as an exception, I might make you a part of his training camp. \NWhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The camp is not for regular players, \Nso the hardness of practices catches up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree! \NCoach, please let me be trained there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided, I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fight! \N- {\i1}Fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Quit muttering to yourself! \NI can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Osu! \N- {\i1}Osu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamakura! \NBack to duty, ya hear me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As always, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oy, Daigo! Who'd think! \NAnd also with some cutie indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You there! \NNo staring 'round!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad you could make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm happy to see you again too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the coach's colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Oka.\NVery glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard a lot about you from Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be used to severe practices, \Nso don't expect any special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised not to complain, \Nthat's why I'm trusting him to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo, are you doing fine?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the moment, to get prepared for my next game, \NI have moved to a remote training camp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so far, \NI am the only girl among all the players here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's enough! \NOne hundred torso lifts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}1! 2! 3! 4!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:22.41,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\i1}6! 7! 8!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I take advantage of my soleness. \NAs it reminds me I should never be weaker than men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every day, as soon as the practice is over, \NI fall down worn out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo, I often wonder, what are you doing now? \NHow is it going in New York?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is it going in Boston? I believe, if it wasn't for those \Nendless thoughts, I couldn't continue doing my best here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rare moments of being free from training \NI usually spend enjoying the quiet Tateshina sceneries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Imagining about Todo being here with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is going this far really worth it, Daigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure of it.\NAnd the sooner we start, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Worries aside. After all, the path we have chosen \Ncannot be completed without the shortcuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! \NListen to me for a second or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our training program \Nis entering the middle stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of competition spirit, \Nwe play against each other from today on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The bouts will be three-set matches. \NBut I will not tolerate inferior play compared to official game!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm announcing the upcoming matchups. \NThe first match of the first day - Takagi vs. Takeyuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The second game. \NFujisaki vs. Mano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The third game. \NNaito vs. Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hesitate. Cause if you fail this interclass practice, \NI'm signing you out of Queen's Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, thanks for the meal, \Nit was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky for you, Naito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is lucky \Nabout defeating a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, coach! I don't stand a single chance. \NThe opponent is a male!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready for any training you recall adequate, \Nand I'm still full of determination! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose today, I'm missing the whole Queen's Cup tournament! \NThis is a complete nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is all that whining about? \NWanna retreat!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been granted \Nwith the opportunity to play here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you betraying everyone again, \Nlike when you rejected the repêchage match!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've already forgotten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider today's game \Nto be your ultimate and final repêchage match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,However mighty the opponent is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you will ever have a better opportunity \Nto prove everyone you are capable of meeting expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or at the very least,\Nto meet {\i1}my{\i0} expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, who once have already dumped tennis away,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,today's match must decide, \Nwhether you are on the start line of a great journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm predetermined? \NWhat if I still lose after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then for Munakata, me and Oka Hiromi everything is over. \NHis life will end for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Match - Fujisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, we move on \Nto the third match of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.43,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Oka \NNaito
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The best of three set match!\NService: Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Naito! \NThis shouldn't take you long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad he ain't as kind fella as I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alright... \NPull yourself together, Hiromi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no right to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever the cost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,30-0!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because if I'm defeated, \Neverything shall be over!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only my tennis...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,40-0!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight, love-game, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... It's but a luck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,First set: 6-0, Naito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? \NWhy making a mess of assured match?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed to me \Nhe wasn't raising you for such a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not over yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not for my tennis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A place like this one...\NA match like this one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will never be suitable to end my path with!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this for real?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can that be happening?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Set: Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Set count: 1-all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps, playing against the ordinary guy \Nwould've been more of a luck...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she really... a woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At such a moment... \NShe makes it a deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's painful... It's excruciating... \NBut even so, I still can't afford to lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever happens to me, \NI can't let everything end here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Advantage: Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Game set!\NAnd... won by Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry, colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be alright. That's just the way Oka \Nis getting used to the court again. Let her lie here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything she could do... She did. \NLet's not take the court away from her that soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Maki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're venturing on the Queen's Cup '90 court!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise! \NEven Midorikawa is participating!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Cannon Serve was revived as a southpaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, do your best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.39,0:23:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This time you don't have the luxury \Nof losing in the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get yourselves together. \NEveryone is watching upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Katsura even makes you use your brand new shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \N"Queen's Cup '90 Begins!"